## 📈 Machine Learning Model

The application uses a supervised regression algorithm to estimate calories burned based on user fitness data.

The model is trained using historical exercise records and evaluated using standard regression metrics to ensure reliable predictions.

---

## 📊 Evaluation Metrics

The model can be evaluated using:

* Mean Absolute Error (MAE)
* Mean Squared Error (MSE)
* Root Mean Squared Error (RMSE)
* R² Score

